<div style="text-align: center;">
<h1 id="toc0"><span>2020冬季征文：“获奖感言”</span></h1>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;">为激励成员，基金会如任何组织一样，会设立各类奖项。这之中既有无数人视作最高荣誉的“基金会之星”，也有其他稍低一级但同样鼓舞人心的褒奖。亦或许，基金会拥有其他秘密的荣誉，甚至是不那么受人欢迎的“奖项”……<br />
这些获奖者，又会作何感想呢？又会说些什么呢？这将由你决定。</span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="background-color: #f2ffcc; font-size: 150%; border: groove 1px #00ff00; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
<p>那么，有请以下三位接受领奖！</p>
<p>第一名（奖金300 RMB）：<a href="/doomsday-con-test">末日竞赛</a>(+134)，由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/infas12" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3416873); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3416873&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583494882" alt="Infas12" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3416873)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/infas12" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3416873); return false;">Infas12</a></span>所写！</p>
<p>第二名（奖金100 RMB）：<a href="/blasphemous">渎神</a>(+80)，由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/old-wall" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2742867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2742867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583494882" alt="Old wall" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2742867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/old-wall" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2742867); return false;">Old wall</a></span>所写！</p>
<p>第三名（奖金100 RMB）：<a href="/neng-luan-tian-zhe-ge-ma">震惊！这个做R18H游戏的也拿了个基金会之星？！</a>(+79)，由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenth-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5226483); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5226483&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583494882" alt="Tenth Lee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5226483)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tenth-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5226483); return false;">Tenth Lee</a></span>所写！</p>
<p>请三位领奖者上台与<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/areyoucrazytom" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1476662); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1476662&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583494882" alt="Areyoucrazytom" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1476662)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/areyoucrazytom" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1476662); return false;">Areyoucrazytom</a></span>获取奖金。</p>
</div>
